reviewText: I think this is a great music for the price. The quality varies in the clips. You have Jos Luis Rodriguez, Wilfrido Vargas, Miguel Gallardo, Juan Pia, El Binomio De Oro, Los Tupamaros & my two favourites Veronica  Castro "Chiquita pero Picosa" & Mana "Perdido en un  Barco".  This is music from the 80's.
